content.rendered:
Masters Tournament Boxing Event at South Eastern Entertainment Centre

Witness the prowess and skill of seasoned boxers at the Masters Tournament Boxing Event, hosted at the South Eastern Entertainment Centre. This event features experienced fighters showcasing their dedication and mastery in the ring. Enjoy an evening of high-caliber boxing, celebrating the enduring spirit and athleticism of our competitors. Join us for a thrilling and inspiring night of boxing excellence!
